Esther Siamfuko bụ onye Zambia na-agba bọọlụ nke na-agbachitere Queens Academy, na mgbazinye site na Choma Warriors, na ndị otu ụmụ nwanyị Zambia.
Siamfuko agbaala bọọlụ maka Choma Warriors na Queens Academy na Zambia.
Siamfuko nọchitere anya Zambia na afọ 2020 COSAFA Women's U17 Championship. O meriri n'ọkwa dị elu na 28 Nọvemba  na afọ 2020 na mmeri enyi na enyi megide Chile.
